UnitLPOracle::fairLPPrice
├── when feeds are configured and the fair price is within the allowed TWAP deviation
│   ├── it returns the Alpha Homora fair LP price
│   └── it is insensitive to reserve ratio manipulation when external prices stay fixed
├── when a required feed is missing
│   └── it reverts
├── when total supply is zero
│   └── it reverts
├── when a feed answer is non-positive
│   └── it reverts
└── when the price guard rejects the price
    └── it reverts with stale price


UnitLPOracle::setFeeds
├── when called by the owner
│   └── it stores both feeds
└── when called by a non-owner
    └── it reverts


UnitLPOracle::setPriceGuard
├── when called by the owner
│   └── it updates the price guard
└── when called by a non-owner
    └── it reverts
